---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Econified" description="Our privacy policy explains how we minimize data collection and ensure all calculations run locally in your browser." noAds={true}>
  <main class="container">
    <div class="glass-panel content-section">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><em>Last updated: 2026</em></p>
      
      <p>
        Econified respects your privacy and is designed to minimize data collection.
      </p>

      <h2>Two Storage Modes</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Local mode (default, no account):</strong> all calculators and decision workflows run locally in your
        browser. The values you enter are not transmitted to our servers. The decision workflow may save your case in
        your browser's local storage so you can continue later on the same device; you can clear it at any time with
        the "Start over" button or by clearing browser data.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Optional cloud workspace:</strong> if you create an account and explicitly press Save, your email
        address and the decision case you saved (titles, scenario numbers, and assumptions you entered) are stored so
        you can continue on another device. Nothing is stored unless you press Save. Account data is hosted on
        Supabase in the European Union (Stockholm region) and protected by per-user access rules. From your account
        page you can export all stored data as JSON or permanently delete your account and all associated data at
        any time.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We do not collect financial data entered into calculators, and analytics events never include salaries,
        amounts, employer names, or the contents of decision cases.
      </p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        Econified may use privacy-friendly analytics to understand general website usage, such as page views and interactions. These analytics do not identify individual users.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        The website may use essential cookies required for site functionality and anonymous analytics.
      </p>
      <p>
        Advertising partners, such as Google AdSense, may use cookies to display relevant advertisements in accordance with their own privacy policies.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Third-party services may collect information according to their respective privacy policies.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For privacy questions, contact:
      </p>
      <p><a href="mailto:info@econified.com">info@econified.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
